extends _layout
block content
  .jumbotron.business
    .container-fluid
      .row
        .col-md-12.text-center
          h1 Business Starter Kit:
          h2 Legal Documents for Small Business

  section.content.alt
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 This Business Starter Kit provides the essential legal documents for small business.
          p This Kit is ideal for time-poor business owners who don’t want to pay expensive legal fees to access the documents essential to the daily running of their business.
          h3 The Business Starter Kit includes:
          +definition(
            'A Partnership Agreement',
            'an essential and often overlooked document governing the relationship and business dealings between you and any business partner/s. Think of it as your safety net should anything go wrong down the track.')

          +definition(
            'An Employment Contract for full-time and part-time Employees',
            'a comprehensive employment contract including provisions relating to Confidentiality, Intellectual Property and Restraint of Trade/Non-Competition.')

          +definition(
            'An Employment Contract for Casual Staff',
            'this contract is specifically for the employment of individuals on a casual basis, providing you with the flexibility to adjust your staffing requirements as needed.')

          +definition(
            'Non Disclosure Agreement',
            'this document is essential for anyone who is discussing or sharing business sensitive or confidential information with a third party. For example when sharing a business idea with a potential investor, or when engaging a developer to develop your idea to a new App. It ensures your business ideas and information remain yours.')

          +definition(
            'Website Terms & Conditions',
            'standard website terms and conditions, perfect for use on business websites.')

      .row
        .col-md-12.text-center
          a.btn.btn-success.btn-addcart.btn-lg.spacer(href="/", target="_blank")
              span.glyphicon.glyphicon-download-alt
              | &nbsp; Download this all inclusive Business Starter Kit for Only $350.

      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 Use this Business Starter Kit if:
          ul
            li You are a business owner or responsible for running a business
            li You are starting a new business
            li You run an  established business but haven’t got all the necessary legal documents

          h3 Benefits of using the Business Starter Kit:
          ul
            li A cost effective way for business owners to access essential legal documents
            li Quick and easy customisation: don’t spend hours filling out forms
            li All the documents available in one kit
            li Easy to follow instructions
            li Use the documents as often as you need
            li Download templates in Word and fill in the highlighted fields

  section.testimony
    .container
      .row
        .head
          h2 Why Australians love The Lazy Lawyer
          p Here's what they have to say.

        .col-md-6
          +feedback(
            'Absolutely impressed with both the legal document package I purchased today and the subsequent customer service I received from Legal123 when I had an issue with the order. Great customer service and thanks heaps. You definitely made my day today.',
            'Emma Schmidt',
            'Managing Director, ACME CO.',
            'test-person.png')

          +feedback(
            'Legal 123 were the only place I could find the paperwork for a holiday rental agreement that applied to us. Very clear and easy to understand.',
            'Kenneth Rodriquez',
            'theislandholidayrentals.com.au',
            'test-person2.png')

